		PRINTFORML [{ARG:1}]%CALLNAME:POS(ARG:1),20% >>>>> 핵열무효화횟수를 전부 파괴！
	ENDIF
	IF 1 > CFLAG:POS(ARG:1):핵열가드킬
		CFLAG:POS(ARG:1):핵열가드킬 = 1
		PRINTFORML [{ARG:1}]%CALLNAME:POS(ARG:1),20% >>>>> 핵열내성을 １턴간 파괴！
	ENDIF
	CALL ATTACK_SINGLE, ARG, POS(ARG:1),3586
ELSE
